OK, sure fine, get techincal on me sheeeeeesh!.

::Shadow Wing::

She smiled. "Flattery will get you everywhere." She nuzzled against 
him.  She entered the base and walked to the CR chamber room.  She 
set him down and opened the doors. She picked him back up and put him 
inside.  She walked out and closed the doors.  She went over to the 
console and started up the chamber.  
She smiled. "Heh, that wolf." he shook her head,"He's nuts sometimes, 
but dang it if he doesn't have my spark wrapped around his little 
finger." she walked over and sat down to wait for him.
